features: MODERN & FARM STYLE- Our coffee table combines the natural grey wash with white; the minimalist design also adds unique rustic aesthetic to your room; square coffee table can complement any modern or rustic rooms, highlighting your personal taste and ideals

STURDY AND PRACTICAL CONSTRUCTION- The grey coffee table is made of particle boards and can hold up to 180 lbs, featuring strong weight capacity; the "X" design frame on both sides increases the sturdiness and brings more farm flair; the adjustable feet protect your floor from scratches, allowing you to decorate anywhere in the room

DOUBLE LAYERS DESIGN- The spacious 2-tier square coffee table not only greatly increases your storage space but also acts as daily workstation, study table, dining table, etc to meet your multiple purposes; the unique semi-open design allows you to easily take knickknacks, decorations, crafts, magazines, etc from both sides

SCRATCH-PROOF AND EASY TO CLEAN- The storage coffee table has a waterproof and scratch-proof wood top, more durable than regular rectangular coffee tables. The easy-to-clean tabletop only needs you to wipe with a dry cloth, reducing your tedious household chores

EASY TO ASSEMBLE- You can quickly and easily assemble the farmhouse coffee table as it boasts of its simple structure and comes with a detailed illustrated user manual and necessary accessories; if you have any questions, we’ll give you a quick reasonable reply sincerely

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Some tips to know in advance: 1.The color of the coffee table is based on the picture taken. Due to the shooting light, the lighting of the environment where the coffee table is located, and the pixels of the mobile phone/computer device, the color of the coffee table will be different. We have tried to restore the color of the coffee table as close to the real color as possible. 2.The installation instructions are attached on the page. If you still have any questions about the installation or other problems, please find us and we will solve them for you as soon as possible. 3.Please tighten the screws during the installation process to ensure that the coffee table is sturdy after installation. 4.Each plate has a corresponding number. Install the plate in the direction corresponding to the number in the manual to avoid incorrect installation. 5.The square coffee tables are inspected and accepted repeatedly before shipment. If there are any parts damaged or missing, please find us and we will solve it as soon as possible.

Sturdy Wooden Construction The stable frame consists of thick well-made boards, featuring excellent weight capacity of 180 lbs and ensures better durability. Large Storage Space Open and half-open storage spaces allow you to freely display or store items. Ideal for living room, study, bedroom, etc. Adjustable Feet Pads Not only increase coffee table stability when the floor is uneven, but also protect your floor from scratches and prevent coffee tables from slidling. Unique Fence Design The coffee table is designed by YITAHOME, with a unique fence and the design of "X", which makes the farmhouse coffee table more stable and noble.

Will grey coffee table be difficult to install? Our product packages and pages come with installation instructions, detailed diagrams to help you install easily. If you have any problems, please find us and we will solve them for you as soon as possible. What's the size of storage coffee table? The center table is a square design, size: 31.5"L x31.5 "W x 17.7" H (80cm x 80cm 45cm), please choose according to the size requirements; You can also refer to other customers' pictures for selection. What are the advantages of this farmhouse table? Grey coffee table is designed by YITAHOME. The fusion of washed ash and fence design makes the rustic coffee table look more beautiful. In addition, the thickened plate makes the coffee table more solid and durable. About screw connections: Use a Phillips screwdriver to tighten, assemble perpendicular to the board and then rotate to tighten. About the method of installing Accessory B Follow the instructions to install A first, then B. Insert B into the hole and rotate it against A. If you can't rotate it, change the direction and rotate it all the way to the end to hold B in place.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Perfect Addition to My Home - 5 Stars!
reviews.reviewText: I couldn’t be happier with my purchase of the rustic farmhouse coffee table! This charming piece has brought an enchanting touch to my living room, transforming it into a cozy haven.First and foremost, the craftsmanship is impeccable. The solid wood construction exudes durability and authenticity, making it a true standout in any rustic-inspired decor. The distressed finish adds character and tells a story of its own, bringing that sought-after vintage charm right into my home.The design is both functional and stylish. With its ample surface area, I can now comfortably entertain guests and display my favorite coffee table books and decorative pieces. The lower shelf is a thoughtful addition, providing extra storage space for magazines, remotes, or even a woven basket for added farmhouse flair.Assembly was a breeze, thanks to the clear instructions and all the necessary hardware provided. The table arrived in perfect condition, a testament to the careful packaging and handling by the seller.All in all, this rustic farmhouse coffee table has exceeded my expectations in every aspect. It’s not just a piece of furniture; it’s an investment that has truly elevated the aesthetics and functionality of my living space. I highly recommend it to anyone in search of a timeless and high-quality addition to their home. Five stars without a doubt!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Arrived on time with no scratches or issues. Easy to setup with good instructions. We bought the matching tv stand so it looks great in the living room. The table is sturdy and has great color. Worth the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The table was easy to assemble, no missing parts and everything fit together perfectly. It looks beautiful in our living room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pros and Cons
reviews.reviewText: Pro: Overall the assembly was pretty straightforward. The table is attractive and serves its purpose.Cons: The screwdriver is "short" and can be difficult to use when attaching multiple screws. The bottom panels did not come with pre-drilled holes to secure the metal brackets. That was difficult if you didn't have a drill. Pre-drilled holes would have been appreciated.The two top panels on the table don't seem to flush. When assembled, one panel was about a 1/4 inch off from the other panel. I'm still trying to figure out why. The bottom panels are fine.The company apologized for the problem and offered a small refund. Great company to work with and very responsive to my emails.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Color. The table is nice.
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to do this review based on the Color. Depends on the lighting! I like it either way. The color here is grey wash. I would say the top of it is more brown. In the right light you can see a hint of grey in it. The sides are not white. It also has a hint of grey. ( lighting is key). It looks great either way. Wasn’t damaged in any way. Is sturdy. Quality is fine. For the price it is excellent. Mine is in a room that doesn’t get used and that is the reason I didn’t spend a fortune. I am pretty impressed and happy with the coffee table. It is exactly what I wanted.

reviews.reviewText: Looks fab, easy to put together and it's nice and solid/sturdy very pleased beautiful quality
Schön anzusehen und gut verarbeitet...Aufbau geht auch leicht..

reviews.reviewTitle: Für den Preis wirklich qualitativ gut
reviews.reviewText: Der Tisch sieht wirklich 100%-ig so aus wie auf dem Bild. Die Anleitung war wirklich einfach und unkompliziert. Alle Löcher waren vorgebohrt und alles hat ohne großen Kraftaufwand zusammen gepasst. Der Tisch ist optisch wirklich schön und wirkt auf mich hochwertig. Steht stabil und da wackelt wirklich gar nichts.Einzig eventuell die geteilte Tischplatte könnte ein Manko sein, weil sich in dieser Ritze gern Dreck ansammelt. Aber im Großen und Ganzen bin ich sehr zufrieden und würde den Tisch auch ein 2. Mal kaufen.
Material und die Verarbeitung sind top und der Aufbau ging Mega schnell.
